# Soukdesigner - API

Souk is the Soukdesigner API allowing customers to integrate their soukdesigner store with any external system like ERP or Stock and Accounting management systems.

## Authentication

Get your API key for the authentication header token `X-Souk-Token` from your Soukdesigner Admin Panel.

