### Create a New Taxonomy [POST]

You may create your own Taxonomy using this action. It takes a JSON object containing a taxonomy section.

+ Request (application/json)

      {
         "taxonomy": {
           "name": "Country"
         }
      }

    + Headers
    
            X-Souk-Token: <your-api-key-from-souk-admin-panel>

+ Response 201 (application/json)

    + Headers

    + Body

              {
                 "id":3,
                 "name":"Country",
                 "root":{
                    "id":9,
                    "name":"Country",
                    "pretty_name":"Country",
                    "permalink":"country",
                    "parent_id":null,
                    "taxonomy_id":3,
                    "taxons":[

                    ]
                 }
              }    

