### Update a Taxonomy [PUT]

For instance, to update a taxonomy's name, make this request:

`PUT /api/taxonomies/1?taxonomy[name]=Pants`

+ Request (application/json)

    + Headers
    
            X-Souk-Token: <your-api-key-from-souk-admin-panel>
            
+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Headers

    + Body

